[2
From: ProMED-mail <promed@promedmail.org>
Source: BBC World News 4 Mar 2001 [edited
France reports FMD antibodies have been found in 9 locations in sheep
imported from Britain. All sheep [recently imported from Britain are to be
slaughtered, together with 30 000 other sheep whose origin cannot be traced
[so could have originated in Britain.
